import React, { Component } from 'react'; class OurHistoryMain extends Component { render() { return (

Alex Clements

Alex is the Father of Dragons. The divorce from Daenerys was difficult. He doesn't like to talk about it.

Ray Greenan

Ray single handedly hunted down every harpy in Britain, which is why you never hear about them. Thanks Ray!

Laura Manson

Hercules didn't kill the Hydra: he just found the body. Laura has 12 Hydra heads mounted on her living room wall at home.

Kevin McEwan

Kevin was once approached by a Sphinx, who threatened to devour him if he could not answer the Sphinx's riddle. Ultimately Kevin's answer was so stupid that the Sphinx lost the will to live and threw itself off of a cliff to it's death.

Jake Thwaites

Scotland's national animal, the unicorn, was almost extinct in it's home country. Thanks to Jake's conservation efforts, the population is now stable. Unfortunately though they are all invisible.
) } } export default OurHistoryMain;
